zej pięćdziesiątki.', 'media_src': 'https://bi.im-g.pl/im/5f/4f/15/z22344799V,Sloane-Stephens.jpg', 'media_desc': 'Sloane Stephens', 'media_type': 'image', 'comments': []}, 'timestamp': 1564053370.743456}}